{
  "id": "adv_group_liz_05_02",
  "title": "LizNoir 05 02",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――リズノワどうしたんだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――What’s up with LizNoir?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.2136871337999997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "最近、全然見なくね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I haven’t seen them around at all lately?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.2136871338,
      "endTime": 5.1228118896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――活動休止とか解散とか噂出てる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――There are rumors going around about them going on hiatus or disbanding.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3228118896,
      "endTime": 9.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "残念だわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a shame.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.7333333333,
      "endTime": 11.6284357071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――マジかよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Seriously?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8284357547,
      "endTime": 13.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "俺、莉央ちゃんと葵ちゃん好きだったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I liked Rio-chan and Aoi-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6,
      "endTime": 16.7924267292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "どのSNSを見ても活動休止とか解散って\n言われてる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It says they’re on hiatus or disbanding\non every site…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.9790934244,
      "endTime": 22.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.9790934244
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "早く私と愛が加入した、新生LizNoirを\n見せつけて驚かせてやりたいよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to show everyone the new LizNoir\nwith Ai and I in it and surprise them~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.8,
      "endTime": 29.7485038534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "……どっちかっていうと、噂通りに\n今はなりそうなんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…If anything‚ it kind of seems\nlike that’s what’s going to happen…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9333333333,
      "endTime": 36.4248294419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "愛、何を弱気なことを言ってるの\n腹筋千回は済んだの～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ why are you being so negative?\nHave you finished your thousand sit-ups~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.5,
      "endTime": 41.574104763499996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "たった今、終わったよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just finished them!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.7666666667,
      "endTime": 44.281315151899996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "だったら、もう千回！\n腹筋をバキバキに割るつもりで！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then do another thousand!\nPut your mind to getting ripped abs!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.4666666667,
      "endTime": 48.3438910961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "ファンに引かれちゃうよ！\nそれより、こころはやってるの？！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The fans will be turned off!\nWhat about you‚ Kokoro?! Are you doing them?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5333333333,
      "endTime": 53.5085941473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "こころは、スマイル担当だから\n身体能力を高める必要はないんです～～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m the smile member‚\nso I don’t need to improve my physical abilities",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7333333333,
      "endTime": 59.933333333300006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "そんな訳ない～～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not true!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1333333333,
      "endTime": 62.225260790200004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "こら、二人とも\n準備運動にどれだけ時間掛けてるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ you two.\nHow much time are you spending on warm-ups?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.4333333333,
      "endTime": 66.87820098409999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 333.3333333999988,
          "startTime": 62.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "次はダンスレッスンだよ、ほら立って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s time for dance lessons next. Come on‚ get up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.0666666667,
      "endTime": 70.3534921329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "おお～、同じメニューをこなした莉央さんと葵さんは\nまったく涼しい顔です。体力オバケ……こほん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oooh‚ Rio-san and Aoi-san are acting all cool\neven after doing the same exercises. Physical monsters… cough",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.5666666667,
      "endTime": 80.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "…………はぁ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………Sigh~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.4333333333,
      "endTime": 81.9637641748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "――って、愛ちゃんが言っていました\nああ、愛ちゃん、先輩方になんて失礼なことを～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――That’s what Ai-chan said.\nOh‚ Ai-chan‚ how could you say something so rude to our seniors~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.2333333333,
      "endTime": 90.1668423824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "私は何も言ってなーい！\nって、あいたた、叫ぶと腹筋が痛い……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn’t say anything~!\nOw‚ ow‚ my abs hurt when I yell…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.3666666667,
      "endTime": 96.7912246625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "……やる気がないなら、僕はもう帰っていいかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…If you don’t have the motivation‚ then can I just go home?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97,
      "endTime": 100.6008615971,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "昨日、もう一度チャンスがほしいって言ったのは\n貴方達なのよ？　やめるなら早い方が私達も――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were the ones who said you wanted another chance yesterday‚\nright? If you’re going to quit‚ the sooner‚ the better for us――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.7666666667,
      "endTime": 108.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "やりますやります！\n待って下さい！　先輩方！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll do it‚ we’ll do it!\nPlease wait! Seniors!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.2333333333,
      "endTime": 111.56618722270001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "そうです、こころは元気ピンピンです\n見て下さい、この華麗なターンを～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right‚ I’m in perfect health.\nLook at this magnificent turn~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7666666667,
      "endTime": 117.2606141986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_05_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "……悪くはないよ\nでも、LizNoirのメンバーとしては……",
      "translations": {
